-----------------------Firebase and Right Database------------------------
link for firebase page and to use Firebase database for this project
https://firebase.google.com/

steps to create Firebase project (database) to use in this module.
1. Goto Firbase.google.com
2. Login with you gmail account
3. See pricing option first
4. Click on Go to console
5. Click Create project and create project
6. create project react-my-burger
7. Then go in to Project Overview->Develop->Realtime Database
8. Click on create database (this create a mongo database in Firebase itself and gives us a API url through which we can post and pull data.)
9. Note down the URL and go to Rules and set read and write properties to true.
10 ApI end point for database for this module is https://react-my-burger-20231.firebaseio.com/

go to the main folder where src, components and other folder present in this project foldr burgerbuuilder
and install the package axios using command npm install --save axios (will use this package to send http requests)

